The "mini-modules" that have multiple inputs might be a little more complicated, but I picture that UI maybe to act like it does when you click on the "add link button" where you edit the content in a popup. Then on the backend we would somehow have to be able to give multiple insertion points
```&lt;figure class="mds_blockquote"&gt;
    &lt;img src="{{image.src}}" alt="{{image.alt}}"&gt;
    &lt;blockquote&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;{{text}}&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/blockquote&gt;
    &lt;figcaption&gt;{{author}}&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;```
